---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle Double Turkey Burrito Bowls with Guacamole and Pickled Jalapeños
description: This bowl packs in all the flavours of a turkey burrito: Mexican-style rice, charred veggies, zippy guac, spicy pickled jalapeños and garlicky, smoky turkey! No tortilla? No problem!
